title: Luck Is a Four-Letter Word, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO57
description: Andy Frisella enjoys cussing; but there's one four-letter word he hates: luck. In this episode of the MFCEO Project, he explains why it's imperative to clean up your language and stop using that dirty word.
